(43, 10, 34, 2, 4, 16, 16, 'Ye are gods', 'Divine Authority and Representation', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine authority where humans are depicted as representatives of God. In John 10:34, the phrase ''Ye are gods'' suggests a shared authority, while Exodus 4:16 indicates that Moses will act as God to Aaron, emphasizing the role of humans as mediators of divine will.', 'theme', 0.46099999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
